program:
move    1024,R0
        nop
        wait_sync 4          # Synchronize sequencers over multiple instruments

    loop:
                   
        play      0,1,486      
        acquire   0,0,4      # Acquire waveforms over remaining duration of acquisition of input vector of length = 16380 with integration weights 0,0
        wait      15894
        move      183,R1     
        nop
        repeatloop:
            wait      1000
            loop      R1,@repeatloop
        wait      620
        loop    R0,@loop

        stop
